  "intent": "Perform automated magnetic bead-based nucleic acid purification using AMPure beads on up to 96 samples. Add specified volumes of water and AMPure beads to samples on magnetic module, incubate for 5 minutes with mixing, engage magnet for 5-minute bead settling, remove supernatant. Execute two sequential ethanol washes at 200\u00b5L each with 0.5-minute incubation and immediate supernatant removal. Air-dry beads for 3 minutes, then elute in 28\u00b5L water with 5-minute incubation and resuspension, finally transferring 25\u00b5L purified product to elution plate.",
